{"tid":1920504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓180名軍人感染武漢肺炎病死","createTime":"2020-03-11T13:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:40:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5c12baab2b38bf74b7fc6b62d49a5b7aef99d7d7","tid":1920504,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157869370723346&amp;set=a.398809003345&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157869370723346%26set%3Da.398809003345%26type%3D3&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=0da5163b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157869370723346&amp;set=a.398809003345&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n「北韓不是『不嚴重』，而是你『不知道』」<br />\n<br />\n北韓到底有沒有爆發武漢肺炎，從來是個謎，華文媒體也鮮有報道他們的疫情實況。<br />\n<br />\n但根據零散及有限的內部消息，例如DailyNK報道截至2月25日為止，北韓境內各地死亡人數及因發燒、咳嗽等疑似症被隔離的病患如下：<br />\n<br />\n平壤：死亡7名，隔離16名<br />\n平安北道新義州：死亡8名，隔離32名<br />\n平安北道龍川：死亡4名，隔離12名<br />\n羅先：死亡2名，隔離15名<br />\n黃海南道海州：死亡2名，隔離7名<br />\n<br />\n共計死亡23名，隔離82名<br />\n<br />\n另外，引述截至3月1日的北韓報道，平安南道及江原道分別有2,420、1,500多名「醫學觀察對象」，平安北道則有3,000多名。換言之，僅平安道、江原道等地已公布者已近7,000之多，其他地方更是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n以上「醫學觀察對象」均不准出門，但據悉並無精密檢查或妥善照顧。同時，為避免首都平壤疫病擴散，政府下令將確診及疑似隔離等病患轉移至別處。<br />\n<br />\nDailyNK在3月9日引述消息跟進報道，今年1-2月，已有約180名北韓軍人因感染武漢肺炎病故，而約有3,700名軍人現正被隔離，據悉他們分別駐守北平壤、慈江道、兩江道及北咸鏡道的中朝邊界或附近。<br />\n<br />\n然而據北韓副公衛部長Kim Hyung Hun在2月27日向黨媒《朝鮮新報》稱，國內並無任何感染個案。一如2003年SARS、2014年伊波拉病毒，2015年MERS，北韓政府同樣無對外公布實際疫情。<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n至於更多關於北韓境內如何應對疫情的實況，可參考如下：<br />\n<br />\nDailyNK: Sources: Almost 200 soldiers have died from COVID-19<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailynk.com/english/sources-almost-200-soldiers-have-died-covid-19/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailynk.com%2Fenglish%2Fsources-almost-200-soldiers-have-died-covid-19%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=056aaf23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailynk.com/english/sources-almost-200-soldiers-have-died-covid-19/</a><br />\n<br />\nDailyNK: Explaining reports of COVID-19 infections deep inside N. Korea<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailynk.com/english/explaining-reports-covid-19-infections-deep-inside-north-korea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailynk.com%2Fenglish%2Fexplaining-reports-covid-19-infections-deep-inside-north-korea%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=3a99a88a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailynk.com/english/explaining-reports-covid-19-infections-deep-inside-north-korea/</a><br />\n<br />\nDailyNK: 朝鮮秘密匯總新冠肺炎患者&hellip;&hellip;「疑似症患者死亡23例」<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16917&amp;cataId=nk00600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.dailynk.com%2Fchinese%2Fread.php%3Fnum%3D16917%26cataId%3Dnk00600&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=26fdd1dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16917&amp;cataId=nk00600</a><br />\n<br />\nDailyNK: 「醫學觀察對象都被隔離不能出門」<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16923&amp;cataId=nk00600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.dailynk.com%2Fchinese%2Fread.php%3Fnum%3D16923%26cataId%3Dnk00600&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=2df59c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16923&amp;cataId=nk00600</a><br />\n<br />\nDailyNK: 「朝鮮為首腦部的安全把平壤的新冠肺炎疑似患者移動到地方」<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16915&amp;cataId=nk00600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.dailynk.com%2Fchinese%2Fread.php%3Fnum%3D16915%26cataId%3Dnk00600&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e3e68cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://china.dailynk.com/chinese/read.php?num=16915&amp;cataId=nk00600</a><br />\n<br />\n38North: Pandemics and Preparation the North Korean Way<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.38north.org/2020/02/eimaabrahamian022020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.38north.org%2F2020%2F02%2Feimaabrahamian022020%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=c241d1fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.38north.org/2020/02/eimaabrahamian022020/</a><br />\n<br />\nRimjingang: N. Korea Notifies Chinese Border Authorities that it Will Shoot &quot;Hostile&quot; Citizens and Smugglers &quot;Without Warning&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.asiapress.org/rimjin-gang/2020/03/recommendations/without-warning/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiapress.org%2Frimjin-gang%2F2020%2F03%2Frecommendations%2Fwithout-warning%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=78297d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.asiapress.org/rimjin-gang/2020/03/recommendations/without-warning/</a><br />\n<br />\nRimjingang: &ldquo;Those who will die, will die&rdquo;: Poverty a Greater Concern than Coronavirus as Regime&rsquo;s Warnings are Met with Public Indifference<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.asiapress.org/rimjin-gang/2020/02/recommendations/coronavirus-int/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiapress.org%2Frimjin-gang%2F2020%2F02%2Frecommendations%2Fcoronavirus-int%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=2ada3955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.asiapress.org/rimjin-gang/2020/02/recommendations/coronavirus-int/</a>"},{"pid":"249da2604d3be8434f0dbfc3247f1e41748c7a6b","tid":1920504,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"標靶藥"},{"pid":"7e4ccf256b129de2425a98143ec089681d358d63","tid":1920504,"uid":178800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"金仔應該處決哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji